<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Two Column Profile Layout</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">

    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }

        .section-box {
            background: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            height: 100%;
        }

        h2 {
            border-bottom: 3px solid #0d6efd;
            display: inline-block;
            padding-bottom: 5px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container py-5">
    <div class="row g-4">

        <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-12">
            <div class="section-box">
                <h2>About Me</h2>
                <p class="mt-3">
                    I am a passionate web developer with a strong interest in building
                    responsive and user-friendly websites using HTML, CSS, JavaScript,
                    and Bootstrap. I enjoy learning new technologies and working on
                    real-world projects.
                </p>
                <p>
                    My goal is to become a full-stack developer and contribute to
                    innovative technology solutions.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-12">
            <div class="section-box">
                <h2>Education</h2>
                <ul class="mt-3">
                    <li><b>BCA</b> – XYZ College (2022-2025)</li>
                    <li><b>HSC</b> – ABC Junior College</li>
                    <li><b>SSC</b> – DEF High School</li>
                </ul>

                <h2 class="mt-4">Experience</h2>
                <ul class="mt-3">
                    <li><b>Web Development Intern</b> – 6 Months</li>
                    <li><b>Freelance Developer</b> – Portfolio & Mini Projects</li>
                    <li><b>College Tech Team Member</b></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</div>

<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>

</body>
</html>
